{
  "stem": "6195.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even though I could hardly walk or keep my head up, and I had diarrhea, and we were wearing the clogs-- which one was always too long and the other was too small-- it was just running right through me.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was a-- what they called the block altester-- the-- the-- the one responsible for the block.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a Polish woman prostitute.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was already too old to be a prostitute, so she was the madam-- hardly looked like one, but in Auschwitz, we all looked the same.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as they say, that saints and prostitutes have got soft hearts, well, she helped me a lot with the-- I told her that I am sick.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know what she was doing?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had a doona, and each time, she ripped out a little bit, because we didn't have toilet paper.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So a credit to her, whoever she was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then she kept telling me all the time, don't tell anybody that you are sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I had [? a hard-- I-- ?] when we got to the train, I was already delirious.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But again, I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had a bench there for-- for them to sit down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put me on a bench.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They poured hot water into my mouth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The girls said they couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was singing away the Polish anthem, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was cursing them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the girls put their hands on my mouth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said, let her talk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When really, they-- of course, they didn't understand Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's another story.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's when Schindler has sent one of his mistresses to Berlin to a-- he has heard-- he asked where the-- where the women are.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And somehow-- and the word-- a word got to him that we are in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
